•GRWM TO GO OUT FOR A SPA DAY•🧖‍♀️✨

Sometimes,life requires us to put everything on hold and prioritize our health. I’ve been there,done that!😅 I’m feeling much better now and I’m excited to reconnect with you all🌸 It’s so kind of you guys to check in on me.thank you for your thoughtfulness!This work is my calling and I couldn’t imagine stopping😊

Alright,coming to GRWM😊I’m not sure if you’ll believe me but I was actually getting ready after a proper 3-month break!😅 I had to search for my belongings as I wasn’t sure where they were.Today,I’m planning a salon day with my friend and wisely decided to have lunch at home.I’m wearing a new dress from @oziss.in which looks really flattering on me.Special thanks to them for including a lining material under the white cotton fabric,a thoughtful touch that’s often overlooked by many clothing brands!The dress is super comfortable and I love re-wearing it again and again.

THANKS FOR WATCHING AND YOUR CONTINUED LOVE,SUPPORT! 🤗
LOTS & LOTS OF LOVE 🫶🏼✨

•PERFECT LIPSTICK SHADES FOR EVERYDAY OFFICE/COLLEGE WEAR💄✨•

I wanted to try @kirobeauty from a long time all that I’ve been hearing about  their lipstick is that they’re very long lasting and they have pretty shades. so I thought I’ll try their new NON STOP AIRY MATTE LIQUID LIPSTICKS,I ordered these two colours & I didn’t have to worry much about whether it’s going to suit me or not because they’re specially made for medium to dusky skin tone✨ after it arrived just when I was leaving for some place I tried their right away that evening and trust me I came back home and slept off without removing it(which rarely happens) & in the morning I wake up and go to washroom and I saw myself in the mirror,the lipstick was still there🤩no smudge or budge,right there,intact.just like a tattoo! Now that’s something we girls want!😁 It’s very rare to get a peta approved and skin care infused makeup so get your hands on this one or tell your guy to get you this for the ‘V’ day!😉 

THANKS FOR WATCHING 🤗✨
